Package it.polimi.ingsw.View

Class ModelPrinter

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.View.ModelPrinter
public class ModelPrinter
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents the part of the model that all clients have locally. It is used by the cli and the gui for drawing. The various methods are mainly used by the CLI since the GUI mainly takes the data
